{"tid":2376472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"若有僱員因「禁足令」而未能上班，政府希望僱主能酌情處理","createTime":"2021-01-22T23:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T01:03:07.000Z","uid":80153,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d13a6d457d15869e0957145e4f13caac2b269fb1","tid":2376472,"uid":80153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T23:42:38.000Z","msg":"根據政府公告指，封區禁足令實施48小時，趕及周一清晨6時左右解封讓市民上班，但未有交代有何方案確保受限疫區內沒有「漏網之魚」，僅表示在正式撤銷相關公告時，政府會另行公佈；又指若有僱員因宣告而未能上班，政府希望僱主能酌情處理，不要扣減員工的薪金和福利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210123/ELSOAQLA3FEOFCOKC3XMVU6XGQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210123%2FELSOAQLA3FEOFCOKC3XMVU6XGQ%2F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5Cvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=656ed258\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210123%2FELSOAQLA3FEOFCOKC3XMVU6XGQ%2F&h=782b6544\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210123/ELSOAQLA3FEOFCOKC3XMVU6XGQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港僱主心諗: 擅自曠工炒得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝政府,炒完錢都唔洗賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2f9124453dbd93312a6fe8c491542fb30eb7c2","tid":2376472,"uid":243175,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T23:45:22.000Z","msg":"咩都希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我究希望中六合彩成世人啦又唔見中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc02fd5f99e19eda0a07fb2448d23dc6d6f0899","tid":2376472,"uid":121546,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T23:45:38.000Z","msg":"希望<br />\n酌情<br />\n比政府搞到返唔到都要人施捨先唔洗炒"},{"pid":"36855c0b233705de56f2c9b631a3bf71eecf4c76","tid":2376472,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T23:46:46.000Z","msg":"有返有錢，冇返冇錢。"},{"pid":"ad74b3479eb3a2fe034d18fd8e9e27d150c4bce2","tid":2376472,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":